<plot>In the United States of America voters have the right to choose their leaders, chose their laws and chose their rights. On November 4, 2008 California voters made a choice regarding the legal status of gay marriages. Right or wrong Proposition 8 represented many things to many people. On Christmas night 2008 Mabel is left alone to contemplate the voter's choice and the effects it has had on her family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104268</url></doc>
